# NAME: Crypto
# AUTHOR: Kevin (kevshen13)
# REPO: https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# DESCRIPTION: Crypto exchanges and crypto-related services rule list for Surge
# UPDATED: 2026-04-04
# MAINTENANCE: Maintain this list by traffic purpose and route behavior.
# RULE: Include exchanges, wallets, custody services, staking services, and crypto workflow domains.
# RULE: Keep broad keyword/domain rules conservative to avoid routing unrelated finance or Web3 traffic.
# RULE: Exclude US-specific sites and services from this list.
# RULE: Put Kraken and other US-only / US-routed crypto brokers into us-brokers.list instead.

# ==================== Binance (Global, exclude Binance.US) ====================
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,binance.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,binance.me
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bnbdstatic.com

# ==================== OKX (Global, exclude US/EU regional sites) ====================
